{"tid":683382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(遵理今次....) Guy Leung 最新抄襲事件揭密","createTime":"2018-05-29T15:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T15:52:15.000Z","uid":97608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b934300b0963542251b548fdf7e7af91aa2a8f","tid":683382,"uid":97608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T15:52:15.000Z","msg":"近排燈塔真係好熱鬧，又上市失敗又老師互鬥<br />\n好戲當然要繼續先過癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次爆大獲既對象仍然係抄襲之王 Guy Leung。<br />\n自從舊年抄襲同校康蛇搞到潛水半年之後，再次出水。<br />\n勢估唔到仲死性不改，繼續抄抄抄！<br />\n<br />\n今日醒左少少唔係100%照Copy，但明顯題目、論據完全一樣<br />\n甚至次序都唔調下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎巴打提供更多線索同埋內幕，來緊幾日繼續爆更大獲野！<br />\n保證好睇過TBB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次又賴助教？ <br />\n最新章程仲講到明全部100%自己做，點解釋 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/234652_94dc29d79e9d8db41dcf9cde968e4371.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F234652_94dc29d79e9d8db41dcf9cde968e4371.png&h=6f091b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一題抄襲：齡記出版社<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/234032_e76a2880cb05357b410f57fe990de4e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F234032_e76a2880cb05357b410f57fe990de4e1.png&h=431f7aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGuy Leung 筆記，一Q樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/234242_62bf1edb36141f114521ec4bb4175579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F234242_62bf1edb36141f114521ec4bb4175579.jpg&h=72eacfbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/234429_134ce63057f068a219a0df338fb0b723.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.es